com.twitter.sdk.android.core

Class GuestCallback<T>

  • Object
    • com.twitter.sdk.android.core.Callback<T>
      • com.twitter.sdk.android.core.GuestCallback<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - success result type (e.g. Tweet, List<Tweet>, etc.)
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    retrofit.Callback<T>

    public class GuestCallback<T>
extends Callback<T>
    GuestCallback is a wrapper callback which clears the AppSession on app or guest auth token errors. GuestCallback should be used when making requests using guest auth.
